Gat stems from gati, which stands for speed in sanskrit. These
compositions experiment extensively  with timing of notes
constrained within few quanta of the theka.  

Thirakwa Gat
------------

dhi kda dhi kda dhin 
dha ge ge nake dhin 

ka thak ge thak dhin 
dha ke trika thin na gena

kita thak thina kena 
tha ke trika thin na kena

ka thak ge thak dhin
dha ke trika dhin na gena

thak thak thak thak thak 

ge tha rana dha ga thak ta kita 
dha trika dhi kita ga dhi gena

dha kathSS  ge S n tha dha 

ge S n tha dha 

ge S n tha dha 









dha ge tita tha ke tita kda dha kda dha kda thak 

thun thun na na na na 

ka tita dha gen tha dha tita dha 
ka tita dha gen tha dha tita dha 
ka tita dha gen tha dha tita dha 




















